Internal chip prevents short circuits so your device and the USB-C charger will not overheat - no fire hazard so you and your home or office are safe from fire and so you also save money from buying replacements for both charger and device.

The chunky plug design of the USB Type C wall charger makes it easy to handle so it can be attached to the socket safely and securely - no electrocution hazard. Charging your device will not be interrupted and you stay connected to the internet whenever you are.

Fold away pins/prongs make sure this spare USB C plug is transported safely - no accidental damage so you save money from buying replacements.

39 inch cable is long so that the device can be placed anywhere - you will be at a safe distance from the socket while simultaneously charging and using your Apple Macbook 13 inch, Google Chromebook Pixel 2, Nokia N1 Tablet, HP Pavilion x2, or any device with a Type-C connection.
